room_title: Escape room "Lost In Time" by Mastermind Escape Games in Chicago
room_address: 1015 E State Pkwy Suite 200 Schaumburg, IL 60173
room_description: You and your friends are stuck in a time-and-space warp! The last thing you remember is you were visiting your loony grandfather, and he was about to show you his latest invention... He turned the garage into a time machine, but haven't worked out the kinks yet. Now, light years away, you must find a way to get back before the machine runs out of power.
